viewof text = Inputs.textarea({label: "Text",value: "0oöäøO|Ll1Iti7'`!#%&/()[]$@*^~<>-:;,_±|?+=agkmnpry\n\nif (result > 5 && x <= 3 | !is.na(x))\n {\n  print('Condition met')\n  } else {\n    print('Condition not met'\n)}"})
```

**Text:** ${text}

```{ojs}
viewof font = Inputs.select(["Inconsolata", "Roboto Mono", "Source Code Pro", "IBM Plex Mono", "JetBrains Mono", "Fira Mono", "Oxygen Mono", "Victor Mono", "Space Mono", "PT Mono", "Noto Sans Mono", "Spline Sans Mono", "Overpass Mono"], {label: "Fonts", multiple: false})
```

**Font:** ${font}

```{ojs}
viewof size = Inputs.range([5, 50], {value: 5, step: 1, label: "Font size"})
```

**Font size:** ${size}px

